  _eventName: 'Autonomous vehicles authorized on the French market: a turning point for mobility'
  _date: September 26, 2024
  _subheading: 'France now permits autonomous vehicles in cities, leading the way in smarter, greener mobility and establishing itself as a European pioneer in transport innovation.'
  _coverImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 63e7cdb0f96db1612b9b3ce7e5ed8081, type: 3}
